<section id="contato" class="section-padding bg-[#84A59D] relative overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/sandpaper.png')] opacity-20"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 text-center lg:px-8">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.6em] text-white/70">
        Agende uma Conversa
      </span>
      <h2 class="mt-10 text-5xl font-medium leading-tight text-white sm:text-7xl italic tracking-tighter">
        Dê o Primeiro Passo <br />
        <span class="not-italic font-normal">Para o Seu Bem-Estar.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-10 text-xl leading-relaxed text-white/80 font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Não precisa carregar tudo sozinho. Vamos conversar e entender como posso te acompanhar nessa jornada de redescoberta.
      </p>
      
      <div class="mt-16 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-10">
        <a href="https://wa.me/5511999999999" target="_blank" class="btn-mindful bg-white text-[#84A59D] hover:bg-[#FAF7F2]">
          Agendar Atendimento
        </a>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-8 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-white/40">
          <span>Presencial • São Paulo</span>
          <span class="h-1 w-1 rounded-full bg-white/40"></span>
          <span>Online • Para todo o mundo</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
